OL,5, A book about the rise and fall of media
OL,6, mogul Robert Maxwell has won best      
OL,7, biography at the Costa Book Awards.    
OL,9,FJudges said John Preston's biography   
OL,10,FFall: The Mystery of Robert Maxwell,   
OL,11,Fwas "epic" and "a unanimous winner".   
OL,13,FJewish publishing tycoon Maxwell       
OL,14,Fescaped Nazi occupation by fleeing to  
OL,15,FFrance as a teenager, later becoming a 
OL,16,FLabour MP and businessman.             
OL,18,FBut on his death, unscrupulous dealings
OL,19,Fand long-hidden debts came to light,   
OL,20,Fhis reputation in tatters.             
